Name: MapsPerformance
Description: This Sample provides the ability to monitor the performance of map objects, breaking down areas into monitored status areas.
Requirements: Must have a Geographic map created.
If map is Georeferenced, the map points should be very far apart.
Instructions: Open maps and select a map.
After selecting a map, all the map objects should be loaded.
Result: The entire map is covered with images of the map objects.
Title: Performance
